        <mxCell id="legend-text" value="9 AI Providers: OpenAI, Claude, Gemini, Groq, Ollama, Mistral, Cohere, LocalAI, Custom | Retry: 3x with exponential backoff (1s, 2s, 4s) | Fallback: Try next provider if primary fails | Circuit Breaker: Disable after 5 consecutive failures&#xa;Colors: Green=Success | Purple=AI Services | Blue=API | Orange=Retry/Events | Red Cylinders=DB | Gray=Files" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=7;" vertex="1" parent="1">
